title: Becoming queen
description:
Becoming Queen.

Documentary about Queen.
"Your presence is requested...
Becoming Queen chronicles the majestic rise of rock&#039;s most flamboyant and revolutionary band. Fronted by Freddie Mercury, Queen blends stylistic elements of hard rock, opera, and Fin Pan Alley to create their own unique tapestry of musical magic.
The program contains extensive interviews with friends, members of pre-Queen outfits, Smile and Ibex/Wreckage, their musical peers, rare archival interviews with band members themselves and scores of previously unseen photos and vintage memorabilia, The show reveals Queen&#039;s regal reign in all its spectacular glory - The Kings of stadium rock and supergroup par excellence!"
